original: Öqvist, Olof Einar, disponent, Göteborg, f. 15/12/93 i Karlstad av fabr. Olof Ö. o. Emelia Andersson. G. 28 m. Rut Robertson. Barn: Ingela f. 29, Britta 33’. — Stud:ex. i Karlstad 12, agronomex. v. Ultuna 16. As’sist. h. lantbr:ing. i Karlstad o. Örebro 17, 18. Lär. v. Älgå lantm:sk. 17-19, förest. 19-21, anst. av Sv. Superfosfat Försäljn. A-B f. konstgödselpropag. 21-28, försälj, f. samma firma 28-42, di’Sp. f. fil. i Gbg fr. 42.
translated: Öqvist, Olof Einar, manager, Gothenburg, b. 15/12/93 in Karlstad, son of factory worker Olof Ö. and Emelia Andersson. Married on 28, spouse's name Rut Robertson. Children: Ingela b. 29, Britta b. 33'. — Completed high school in Karlstad in 12, agricultural degree from Ultuna in 16. Assistant in agricultural engineering in Karlstad and Örebro in 17, 18. Teacher at Älgå agricultural school from 17-19, supervisor from 19-21. Employed by Swedish Superphosphate Sales AB for fertilizer propaganda from 21-28, continued sales for the same company from 28-42, appointed manager for the company in Gothenburg from 42.
